    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Welcome to &quot;Airplanes Dogfight Racer&quot;, an exciting air racing and battle game where winning is all about conquering the skies! Compete against other airplanes as enemies while completing the race and engaging in intense dogfights. With 5 different weapons to choose from, you can use your machine gun, missiles, mines, shield, and repair kits to emerge victorious.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1778040/extras/411038020af162fc26a4001b63acb71c.poster.avif?t=1727849191\" width=690 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1778040/extras/411038020af162fc26a4001b63acb71c.webm?t=1727849191\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1778040/extras/411038020af162fc26a4001b63acb71c.mp4?t=1727849191\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Game Features</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game features alternative routes that offer strategic advantages, making the air race even more thrilling. Choose from three gameplay modes - Championship, Arcade, and Time Trial - and test your skills in solo or multiplayer split-screen modes. The game's difficulty levels, ranging from easy to hard, make it a perfect fit for both novice and expert players.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Five Heart-Pounding Race Tracks &amp; 8 High-Flying Airplanes Await!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With five different tracks to unlock, as well as a garage where you can purchase eight different types of airplanes, &quot;Sky Carnage: Aerial Anarchy&quot; offers endless hours of entertainment. The unlock system allows you to unlock new items and tracks as you progress, keeping the game fresh and exciting.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1778040/extras/def162419c3e9938b1bc374a4c3c47b0.poster.avif?t=1727849191\" width=690 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1778040/extras/def162419c3e9938b1bc374a4c3c47b0.webm?t=1727849191\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1778040/extras/def162419c3e9938b1bc374a4c3c47b0.mp4?t=1727849191\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Game Features Made Easy: Fly Planes, Boosters, Enemies, Weapons, and Local Leaderboards!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game's features include an airplane controller, booster cooldown system, enemy AI, and a dogfight system with five weapons. With a local leaderboard, you can compete with your friends and local rivals for the top spot.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1778040/extras/cec6d9797b1943a6adc3d88b09f2eebc.poster.avif?t=1727849191\" width=690 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1778040/extras/cec6d9797b1943a6adc3d88b09f2eebc.webm?t=1727849191\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1778040/extras/cec6d9797b1943a6adc3d88b09f2eebc.mp4?t=1727849191\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game also includes a countdown system, which adds to the excitement and adrenaline rush. With all these amazing features, &quot;Sky Carnage: Aerial Anarchy&quot; is a game that you can't afford to miss. So, what are you waiting for? Download the game now and soar to victory in the skies!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1778040/extras/c0608e72f97c492d44964cbca5699768.poster.avif?t=1727849191\" width=690 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1778040/extras/c0608e72f97c492d44964cbca5699768.webm?t=1727849191\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1778040/extras/c0608e72f97c492d44964cbca5699768.mp4?t=1727849191\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
